node.text: Hazel helped me show off the new Navigator Series line of bags from @Nomatic !  I love Nomatic bags, because they check all of the boxes of what I'm looking for in a bag.  I feel like they just think of everything!  1 day left on this kickstarter, to get the early adopter pricing!  Don't sit on this one. Follow the link in my bio to see all of the awesome features.

node.title: LEGIT KICKSTARTER FROM @NOMATIC !  1 DAY LEFT! Link in my BIO

node.text: Are you going through something that feels like a mess. Like your life is in chaos?  I’ve been there and still do from time to time. God lauded this on my heart today and just wanted to share this little piece of insight on trials and struggles and how it relates to faith.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Adam Busby on August 23, 2021 tagging @byltbasics. May be an image of 1 person, beard, biceps and standing.

node.text:
Routine…. Have you found it easier to get back in a fitness routine once the kids are back in school?  I feel like our life is back to normal now that the kids are back. Consistently going to bed at an earlier time and waking up at a set time has helped tremendously! 
Also, have you tried gym shorts with liners in them?  LIFE CHANGING!  @byltbasics 
#BYLTforTHIS #itsabuzzworld #outdaughtered  #gym

node.text:
We had a fun little day at the Houston Galleria with Riley and Olivia. @dbusby needed to find a dress for an upcoming charity event, so we took the opportunity to make a fun one out of it for the two munchkins. 
 First photo context:  I’m always joking with Olivia that we are best friends and she gets so embarrassed and tries to not hold my hand.  #ifsabuzzworld #outdaughtered

node.text: Today was one of those divide and conquer days, with @dbusby and i both having errands to get done. I took Parker to run around Houston with me and of course she got a fun treat, to make the day memorable. It’s always a challenge giving our kids one on one attention, but we always seek out these opportunities to do it!  #itsabuzzworld #outdaughtered  #byltforthis @byltbasics
